00:00:04.820 --> 00:00:08.325
Welcome to this lesson on Excel modeling.

00:00:08.325 --> 00:00:12.330
This lesson will build nicely on the business metric lesson.

00:00:12.330 --> 00:00:16.640
Now that you know how to calculate and interpret a business metric,

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:19.565
you can start forecasting the key metrics.

00:00:19.565 --> 00:00:21.470
By the end of this lesson,

00:00:21.470 --> 00:00:26.675
you will understand the fundamentals of sales and financial forecasting models.

00:00:26.675 --> 00:00:31.415
This lesson will prepare you nicely for the project at the end of the lesson.

00:00:31.415 --> 00:00:35.780
