00:00:35.780 --> 00:00:42.185
the New York Stock Exchange to forecast out a P&amp;L statement for a company of your choice.

00:00:42.185 --> 00:00:47.030
The data will include financial performance data from over 500 companies.

00:00:47.030 --> 00:00:48.470
By the end of the course,

00:00:48.470 --> 00:00:51.910
you will have mastered how to use advanced Excel tools,

00:00:51.910 --> 00:00:55.430
and this will set you up nicely for completing the project.

00:00:55.430 --> 00:00:57.440
So, let's get started.

